A mere 20 minutes’ drive from Cape Town, Durbanville is energetically becoming Cape Town’s hub for business and leisure. With its central location, Durbanville offers world-class medical centres, education facilities, accompanied by award-winning scenic wineries, restaurants, and shopping centres.  Medical Office Suites 17 On Somerset inspires to deliver with its centrality, modern architecture and cutting-edge medical office suites. These suites are distinctively designed for medical and wellness professionals in mind. Phase 1 comprises of 9 unique opportunities that range between 91m2 and 162m2. The medical office suites are located within walking distance to Durbanville Medi-Clinic, Advanced Surgical Centre and Ampath Laboratory, 17 On Somerset offers the buyer value-added service amenities such as: Medical Lift, Medical Waste Room, Standby Generator, Fibre internet, Air-conditioning and biometric gated access.  17 On Somerset distinguishes itself through distinctive curated finishes which include: Porcelain tiled reception, kitchen, and bathrooms. Office floors to be overlaid by Belgotex Berber Point. Geberit flush mounted sanitary wares and basins fitted with Hans Grohe mixers. 17 On Somerset is truly a bespoke development, taking medical suites to the next level. For more information contact Urban Town Property Studio Johan at 082 628 5028 or Louis at 076 978 7360